00:31:38.102 --> 00:31:41.252
sometimes up to 20% of the cells being

531
00:31:41.282 --> 00:31:45.082
deficient for the tumor to be recognized fully by the immune system.

532
00:31:45.792 --> 00:31:49.762
So energized by this, we went forward with this approach, and

533
00:31:49.802 --> 00:31:52.402
we started to consider the possibility that we would use

534
00:31:53.682 --> 00:31:57.182
